<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Happy 25th Birthday ❤️</title>

<style>
*{
margin:0;
padding:0;
box-sizing:border-box;
font-family:'Segoe UI',sans-serif;
}

body{
background:#ffffff;
color:#333;
text-align:center;
}

.hero{
height:100vh;
display:flex;
flex-direction:column;
justify-content:center;
align-items:center;
padding:20px;
}

h1{
font-size:3rem;
margin-bottom:20px;
color:#d46a92;
}

.subtitle{
font-size:1.2rem;
max-width:700px;
line-height:1.8;
}

.btn{
margin-top:30px;
padding:15px 30px;
background:#d46a92;
color:white;
border:none;
border-radius:30px;
cursor:pointer;
font-size:1rem;
}

section{
padding:80px 20px;
}

.memory{
max-width:800px;
margin:auto;
}

.memory h2{
color:#d46a92;
margin-bottom:20px;
}

.question{
background:#fafafa;
padding:25px;
border-radius:20px;
max-width:600px;
margin:20px auto;
}

input{
padding:12px;
width:80%;
margin-top:15px;
border:1px solid #ddd;
border-radius:10px;
}

.final{
display:none;
padding:80px 20px;
}

.final h2{
font-size:2.5rem;
color:#d46a92;
margin-bottom:20px;
}

.heart{
font-size:3rem;
animation:beat 1s infinite;
}

@keyframes beat{
50%{transform:scale(1.2);}
}
</style>
</head>

<body>

<div class="hero">
<h1>Happy 25th Birthday ❤️</h1>

<p class="subtitle">
Today is all about you.
I wanted to create something special that could make you smile,
even if only for a few minutes.
</p>

<button class="btn" onclick="scrollToQuestions()">
Start Your Surprise
</button>
</div>

<section class="memory">
<h2>A Little Message For You</h2>

<p>
You have been through so much lately,
and I know things haven't always been easy.
I just wanted you to know that you are loved,
appreciated and deeply special to me.
I hope this birthday brings you happiness,
peace and everything your heart deserves.
❤️
</p>
</section>

<section>
<h2 style="color:#d46a92;">Answer These Questions</h2>

<div class="question">
<p>What is my favorite color?</p>
<input id="q1">
</div>

<div class="question">
<p>Who loves you the most?</p>
<input id="q2">
</div>

<button class="btn" onclick="checkAnswers()">
Unlock Final Surprise
</button>
</section>

<div class="final" id="final">
<div class="heart">❤️</div>

<h2>You Did It!</h2>

<p style="max-width:700px;margin:auto;line-height:2;">
Happy Birthday, my love.

No matter how many birthdays pass,
I hope I get to celebrate every single one with you.

Thank you for being you.

I love you more than words can explain.
❤️
</p>
</div>

<script>
function scrollToQuestions(){
window.scrollTo({
top:900,
behavior:'smooth'
});
}

function checkAnswers(){

let q1=document.getElementById("q1").value.toLowerCase();
let q2=document.getElementById("q2").value.toLowerCase();

if(q1 && q2){
document.getElementById("final").style.display="block";
document.getElementById("final").scrollIntoView({
behavior:"smooth"
});
}
else{
alert("Answer the questions first ❤️");
}
}
</script>

</body>
</html>
